You are required to develop and validate a registration form 
[using ReactJS] containing following elements;

Full Name – At least 6 characters long
Username – No spaces
Email – Valid email
Year of Birth – At least 15 years old
Mobile Number– Contains only numbers
Gender – Validate for selection
Country – Validate for selection
Register – button

All the elements of the form will have meaningful placeholder 
and if not validated show an error in front of the element.